---
description: React components — UI layer with client/server component patterns
globs:
  - src/components/**
  - src/app/**/page.tsx
  - src/app/**/layout.tsx
---

Component conventions:
- Client Components must use `'use client'` directive
- Use `useActionState` for form submissions to Server Actions
- Use `useOptimistic` for immediate UI feedback (see `history-gallery.tsx`)
- Zustand stores for client state (`src/stores/`) — not React Context
- CSS: Tailwind 4 utilities with `cn()` from `@/lib/utils` for conditionals
- Icons: `lucide-react`
- UI primitives: Radix UI via shadcn/ui in `src/components/ui/`
- Images: use `getDisplayableImageUrl()` — never hardcode `/uploads/` paths
- `params` and `searchParams` are async in page/layout components — always `await`
